"Veri yalnızca tarayıcıda (localStorage) tutulur, sunucuya yazılmaz."
msgstr ""
"Shows shortcuts to the pages the user has pinned and recently visited. "
"Provides quick access to frequently used pages. Data is kept only in the "
"browser (localStorage) and is not written to the server."

#: ⁨system_cards.description (DB)⁩
msgid ""
"Aktif faaliyet sayısı, gecikmiş faaliyet sayısı ve bu çeyrekte kapanan "
"faaliyet sayısını gösteren mini kart."
msgstr ""
"Mini card showing the number of active activities, overdue activities, "
"and activities closed this quarter."

